We are in those days of Noah, folks. We

00:27:46.549 --> 00:27:46.559
are

00:27:46.559 --> 00:27:49.190
in that time of the end.

00:27:49.200 --> 00:27:51.669
I believe with all my heart that

00:27:51.679 --> 00:27:53.750
Jesus Christ is coming and he is coming

00:27:53.760 --> 00:27:56.149
soon. You say, "Well, Brandon,

00:27:56.159 --> 00:27:58.070
why do you say about Prince

00:27:58.080 --> 00:28:00.710
George, the little boy, and he is going

00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:02.549
to be a part of the

00:28:02.549 --> 00:28:02.559
Antichrist?"The

00:28:02.559 --> 00:28:05.190
Antichrist reigns for seven years:

00:28:05.200 --> 00:28:07.830
three and a half years of not so bad,

00:28:07.840 --> 00:28:10.149
three and a half years of hell on earth.

00:28:10.159 --> 00:28:11.750
But either way, it's seven years. He's

00:28:11.750 --> 00:28:11.760
12.

00:28:11.760 --> 00:28:15.669
I didn't say he would be

00:28:15.679 --> 00:28:17.430
king;

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:19.830
I didn't say I saw him being king. I

00:28:19.840 --> 00:28:21.830
said he would have more influence than

00:28:21.840 --> 00:28:25.029
his father would have.

00:28:25.039 --> 00:28:29.909
I saw the king now—not there, gone.

00:28:29.919 --> 00:28:31.750
Whether he passes away or not, I don't

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:34.070
know. I can't add to or take away from

00:28:34.080 --> 00:28:35.510
anything, but I saw he was no longer

00:28:35.520 --> 00:28:39.590
there. I saw William doing it, and I saw

00:28:39.600 --> 00:28:44.149
his son had more influence than he does.

00:28:44.159 --> 00:28:48.950
His voice was louder as he gets older

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:51.590
than his father's will have.

00:28:55.760 --> 00:28:57.750
His father was more passive than

00:28:57.760 --> 00:29:01.029
him. And I saw in this vision

00:29:01.039 --> 00:29:03.750
in this time of prayer yesterday or

00:29:03.750 --> 00:29:03.760
the

00:29:03.760 --> 00:29:06.070
day before that he would rise

00:29:06.080 --> 00:29:09.110
up and take rule, but he would be

00:29:09.120 --> 00:29:12.149
not as bold as what his son

00:29:12.159 --> 00:29:14.389
would be and more of somebody

00:29:14.399 --> 00:29:17.750
that was dark like Harry Potter

00:29:17.760 --> 00:29:20.710
in the days ahead. There was a black

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:23.110
cloak around him.

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:25.510
And I said, 'That's interesting.'And I saw

00:29:25.520 --> 00:29:28.630
the number seven beside him. And then I

00:29:28.640 --> 00:29:31.350
saw 2026 and it was set in stone

00:29:31.360 --> 00:29:33.590
with fruit hanging from it. And I said,

00:29:33.600 --> 00:29:34.710
'What does that mean?'The Lord said,

00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:37.510
'It's set in stone.'Great change is

00:29:37.520 --> 00:29:39.830
coming to the royal family concerning

00:29:39.840 --> 00:29:41.669
the signs of the times and the coming of

00:29:41.679 --> 00:29:43.669
the Lord Jesus Christ. In the days

00:29:43.679 --> 00:29:46.230
ahead, you're going to see great change

00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:49.590
in that family

00:29:49.600 --> 00:29:52.549
in 2026, 2027. You're going to see

00:29:52.549 --> 00:29:52.559
it

00:29:52.559 --> 00:29:54.710
morphing, a changing.

00:29:54.720 --> 00:29:59.269
And I saw that young man rising up

00:29:59.279 --> 00:30:01.350
and I thought, 'What is that

00:30:01.350 --> 00:30:01.360
about?'But

00:30:01.360 --> 00:30:04.230
we hear in part, see in part.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:08.389
All I know is I saw change coming

00:30:08.399 --> 00:30:10.710
and it was interesting. So I've been

00:30:10.720 --> 00:30:12.230
just praying over things and

00:30:12.240 --> 00:30:15.110
piecing things together.

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:16.950
And the only thing I can tell you, the

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:19.190
most important thing I can say tonight

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:21.510
is you need to be sold out to

00:30:21.520 --> 00:30:23.110
Jesus.

00:30:23.120 --> 00:30:25.669
You need to be having your lamps full of

00:30:25.679 --> 00:30:28.870
oil. You need to be seeking him daily,

00:30:28.880 --> 00:30:31.029
not just on Sundays.

00:30:31.039 --> 00:30:33.110
You need to be intimate with the Father

00:30:33.120 --> 00:30:35.990
and the Father intimate with you. It's

00:30:36.000 --> 00:30:39.190
time to get serious about the

00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:41.190
Father's business and the coming of our

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:43.029
Lord

00:30:43.039 --> 00:30:48.230
like never before. We must wake up.

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:51.669
Churches must preach repentance and

00:30:51.679 --> 00:30:53.909
holiness and coming to the Father and

00:30:53.919 --> 00:30:56.230
not being lukewarm. We

00:30:56.230 --> 00:30:56.240
must

00:30:56.240 --> 00:30:58.950
be hot.

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:02.149
We must not be cold or lukewarm;

00:31:02.159 --> 00:31:03.669
he'll spew you out of his mouth. We

00:31:03.679 --> 00:31:05.190
need to be hot for Jesus is what I'm

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:07.269
trying to tell y'all.

00:31:07.279 --> 00:31:10.310
It's not time to be church as usual; it's

00:31:10.320 --> 00:31:13.029
time to be church unusual. Being the

00:31:13.029 --> 00:31:13.039
salt

00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:16.389
because we've lost our saltiness,

00:31:16.399 --> 00:31:19.269
we must be the mouthpiece in this earth

00:31:19.279 --> 00:31:21.590
telling and being that one watching on

00:31:21.600 --> 00:31:23.590
the wall crying out and telling people

00:31:23.600 --> 00:31:25.590
with all that we have, like John the Baptist

00:31:25.600 --> 00:31:28.070
did, that Jesus is here. He's

00:31:28.080 --> 00:31:31.269
coming.

00:31:31.279 --> 00:31:33.430
It's time to repent.

00:31:33.440 --> 00:31:36.789
It's time to get your heart right.

00:31:36.799 --> 00:31:38.389
And I say that over and over and over

00:31:38.399 --> 00:31:39.990
again, but I feel like

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:41.190
after a while you feel like you're a

00:31:41.200 --> 00:31:43.190
broken record. But it's like being

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:46.950
serious about this year in 2026.

00:31:46.960 --> 00:31:49.430
Wake up. You've got three days left to

00:31:49.440 --> 00:31:51.029
get what you wanted to do

00:31:51.039 --> 00:31:55.110
in 2025 done. Now it's two.

00:31:55.120 --> 00:31:58.630
Today's over. You got two days left.

00:31:58.640 --> 00:32:00.230
What will you do with these last two

00:32:00.240 --> 00:32:03.029
days, this last 48 hours? What will we see? Will we see anything in New Orleans? Will we see anything? I pray we don't. Like I told you, I believe our job is to stop things. We're

00:32:03.029 --> 00:32:03.039
the salt. Even with the prayer groups we have at church, the people we talk to, you know, there's people that take prayer real serious and there's people that just kind of go,

00:32:03.039 --> 00:32:07.190
'I'm here for entertainment.'I was told, 'You need to say this is for entertainment purposes only.'You know what, folks? I don't look at this as entertainment. I look at this as a job. This is a calling that we are called for such a time as this to bring forth prayer for the nations. I'm not here to entertain you. You can watch this and you think, 'I have nothing to do with my time; I want to go see what the bald-headed guy is saying is coming.'I'm here to call you to an arms of prayer.

00:32:07.200 --> 00:32:09.110
And if you want to take it seriously and

00:32:09.120 --> 00:32:11.269
pray with me, I would greatly appreciate

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:13.669
it. If not, I would advise you probably to click off and go watch somebody else that's going to entertain you. I'm here to tell you

00:32:13.679 --> 00:32:15.909
what I believe the Holy Spirit has told

00:32:15.919 --> 00:32:18.870
me is coming.

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:21.269
Am I human? I can miss it. Yes, we all

00:32:21.279 --> 00:32:24.070
can. People say, 'Well, no prophets in

00:32:24.080 --> 00:32:25.990
the Bible missed it.'I'm not a prophet

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:29.110
in the Bible. I

00:32:29.120 --> 00:32:31.350
read it through and I

00:32:31.360 --> 00:32:33.590
see what they said, and

00:32:33.600 --> 00:32:35.830
my whole job and my whole heart is

00:32:35.840 --> 00:32:38.310
to line up with Jesus.

00:32:38.320 --> 00:32:39.830
I don't want to compare myself to

00:32:39.840 --> 00:32:43.029
somebody else. I say, 'Hey, I want to be

00:32:43.039 --> 00:32:45.669
more like him.'And does Brandon have

00:32:45.679 --> 00:32:48.950
issues? Yes. Does Brandon have faults?

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:53.190
Yes. Can Brandon miss it? Yes.

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:55.190
All I know is I'm doing the best I

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:57.669
can with what I have.

00:32:57.679 --> 00:33:00.070
And I appreciate every one of you, all

00:33:00.080 --> 00:33:02.789
5,500 of you right now watching saying,

00:33:02.799 --> 00:33:04.870
'Hey, we take you serious and we

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:06.950
want to pray with you as you see what we

00:33:06.960 --> 00:33:09.269
saw in the

00:33:09.269 --> 00:33:09.279
news.'Fruit

00:33:09.279 --> 00:33:12.230
is important.

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:14.070
So, we're going to pray again tonight

00:33:14.080 --> 00:33:15.990
and we're going to seek him and we're

00:33:16.000 --> 00:33:18.070
going to find him. I believe that the

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:19.909
Bible says that those that seek me will

00:33:19.919 --> 00:33:21.909
find me. Those that knock, I'll open the

00:33:21.919 --> 00:33:24.630
door for them.

00:33:24.640 --> 00:33:26.230
And so, I'm thankful for every single

00:33:26.240 --> 00:33:28.230
one of you. We take communion, we pray,

00:33:28.240 --> 00:33:30.630
we worship. And I try to make Jesus as

00:33:30.640 --> 00:33:34.630
real to you as what he is to me,

00:33:34.640 --> 00:33:36.470
showing you the way that you have the

00:33:36.480 --> 00:33:38.549
ability to find him and touch the

00:33:38.549 --> 00:33:38.559
hem

00:33:38.559 --> 00:33:40.310
of his garment just like anybody else

00:33:40.320 --> 00:33:42.630
does. He is no respecter of

00:33:42.640 --> 00:33:45.590
persons, but he is a respecter of faith.

00:33:45.600 --> 00:33:47.990
Do you believe? Are you a believing

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:51.509
believer? Are you a doubter?

00:33:51.519 --> 00:33:53.430
And I just want to be that person that

00:33:53.440 --> 00:33:55.669
when I get up on the other side, he

00:33:55.679 --> 00:33:58.950
says, 'Brandon, you did good. Enter into

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:02.870
my rest. Well done. Thank you

00:34:02.880 --> 00:34:05.750
for trying so hard.'It's like

00:34:05.750 --> 00:34:05.760
Kuhlman

00:34:05.760 --> 00:34:08.629
always said, 'Lord Jesus, I really

00:34:08.639 --> 00:34:11.109
tried.'I

00:34:11.119 --> 00:34:14.230
left it all on the court. I may not

00:34:14.240 --> 00:34:15.990
have been the best basketball player. I

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:17.349
may have not have been the best football

00:34:17.359 --> 00:34:19.430
player, but I left everything I could on

00:34:19.440 --> 00:34:20.950
the field.

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:23.190
I didn't hold nothing back. I gave it

00:34:23.200 --> 00:34:26.470
all I had.

00:34:26.480 --> 00:34:28.550
I've been obedient and doing

00:34:28.560 --> 00:34:30.149
everything he's asked. Don't ask my

00:34:30.159 --> 00:34:33.109
people for nothing. Go on

00:34:33.119 --> 00:34:35.750
YouTube and tell them I'm coming and

00:34:35.760 --> 00:34:37.829
pray and tell them that they need

00:34:37.839 --> 00:34:40.069
to repent and get right with me

00:34:40.079 --> 00:34:41.589
because they're going to hell if they

00:34:41.599 --> 00:34:44.869
don't. And I've done exactly that.

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:48.550
I told Diana as we close out this

00:34:48.560 --> 00:34:52.389
year, 'Do you want to keep going, baby?

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:55.030
Do you want to keep doing this? This

00:34:55.030 --> 00:34:55.040
is

00:34:55.040 --> 00:34:57.109
a lot of

00:34:57.119 --> 00:34:59.990
pressure.'And

00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:02.230
as I sat there

00:35:02.240 --> 00:35:04.069
and we prayed about it, she goes,

00:35:04.079 --> 00:35:05.910
'Hun, I'm in it with whatever you want

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:07.829
to do.

00:35:07.839 --> 00:35:10.630
I'll back you. We'll be a family and

00:35:10.640 --> 00:35:12.390
we'll keep going down this road if this

00:35:12.400 --> 00:35:14.230
is what God's called us to

00:35:14.240 --> 00:35:17.589
do.'And

00:35:17.599 --> 00:35:19.349
as I sat there, the Lord

00:35:19.359 --> 00:35:20.870
said, 'Do you want to keep doing

00:35:20.870 --> 00:35:20.880
it?'I

00:35:20.880 --> 00:35:24.550
said, 'Yeah, I'll help you. I'm sold

00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:28.150
out, but I don't want it to affect my

00:35:28.160 --> 00:35:30.710
relationship with you.'And not only

00:35:30.720 --> 00:35:32.230
that, I don't want to let any of

00:35:32.240 --> 00:35:34.069
these people down if I have anything

00:35:34.079 --> 00:35:35.589
inside of me that needs to be

00:35:35.599 --> 00:35:38.390
cleaned up. There's so

00:35:38.400 --> 00:35:39.910
many people watching.

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:41.670
I see

00:35:41.680 --> 00:35:44.230
people all the time now.

00:35:44.240 --> 00:35:45.910
I can't go in public without being

00:35:45.920 --> 00:35:47.670
noticed,

00:35:47.680 --> 00:35:48.950
especially in our area. It's

00:35:48.960 --> 00:35:51.430
absolutely incredible.

00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:53.270
And I'm so grateful for every single one

00:35:53.280 --> 00:35:54.950
of you. There's so many of you that

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:57.910
are so nice and you're so inquisitive.

00:35:57.920 --> 00:36:00.550
Some of you are rude, but I'm

00:36:00.560 --> 00:36:02.470
thankful for the nice ones. I met a nice

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:05.109
man today. People

00:36:07.119 --> 00:36:09.510
just want to know. But I have a

00:36:09.520 --> 00:36:13.349
treasure in an earthen vessel

00:36:13.359 --> 00:36:14.790
that the excellence of the power is

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:17.670
known of him and not of me. You can do

00:36:17.680 --> 00:36:19.910
it, too. You just got to seek him and

00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:21.990
you find him.

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:24.230
So, I say all that just to love on y'all

00:36:24.240 --> 00:36:25.750
today.

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:28.150
You know, there's a lot of things I want

00:36:28.160 --> 00:36:31.270
to change in 2026 and being

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:34.470
more for y'all to pray

00:36:34.480 --> 00:36:37.829
and do things. People are inviting me

00:36:37.839 --> 00:36:39.510
to come to their churches and preach and

00:36:39.520 --> 00:36:42.069
do things. I probably will take a lot

00:36:42.079 --> 00:36:44.950
of those engagements this year. I feel

00:36:44.960 --> 00:36:47.990
in my heart to go and teach

00:36:48.000 --> 00:36:50.950
prayer at your churches. I don't

00:36:50.960 --> 00:36:52.390
really know what that looks like for

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:54.710
Brandon. I've never seen myself as a

00:36:54.720 --> 00:36:57.510
public speaker; I just talk behind a

00:36:57.520 --> 00:37:00.390
lens. And it's easy to look at a camera

00:37:00.400 --> 00:37:02.069
now because I've gotten used to it. But

00:37:02.079 --> 00:37:04.150
when I get in front of a crowd, it makes

00:37:04.160 --> 00:37:07.109
you real nervous, and so I'm not used to

00:37:07.119 --> 00:37:09.910
that. So I'm thankful that

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:11.349
Jesus would give me the strength to do

00:37:11.359 --> 00:37:12.790
that just like I talked to this camera

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:14.230
before. This was really awkward. I

00:37:14.240 --> 00:37:15.910
practiced and practiced and practiced,

00:37:15.920 --> 00:37:19.829
and so now it's not too bad. I

00:37:19.839 --> 00:37:22.630
feel like it's getting easier,

00:37:22.640 --> 00:37:24.390
and it's weird because, you know,

00:37:24.400 --> 00:37:26.390
there's 5,000 some odd people here and

00:37:26.400 --> 00:37:27.990
that's a lot looking

00:37:28.000 --> 00:37:30.950
at behind a camera. But

00:37:30.960 --> 00:37:33.190
isn't Jesus wonderful that he would take

00:37:33.200 --> 00:37:36.790
somebody like me and do what he's done?

00:37:36.800 --> 00:37:39.750
I'm so grateful for everyone and all

00:37:39.760 --> 00:37:42.150
the Christmas people coming out and

00:37:42.160 --> 00:37:43.829
Christmas cards—all the

00:37:43.839 --> 00:37:45.349
kindness.

00:37:45.359 --> 00:37:46.790
You know, there's so many good people

00:37:46.800 --> 00:37:48.790
that have tried to reach out and just

00:37:48.800 --> 00:37:50.710
love on us this Christmas season, and I

00:37:50.720 --> 00:37:53.349
just want to say thank you. Thank

00:37:53.359 --> 00:37:55.430
you from the bottom of my heart from

00:37:55.440 --> 00:38:00.069
Canada to Japan to South Korea, to so

00:38:00.079 --> 00:38:02.390
many people that have written letters

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:04.230
just saying that you support us and

00:38:04.240 --> 00:38:08.870
pray for us. It means so much.

00:38:08.870 --> 00:38:08.880
Australia—I

00:38:08.880 --> 00:38:14.390
mean the

00:38:14.390 --> 00:38:14.400
islands—it's

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:18.630
incredible. It truly is to see so many

00:38:18.640 --> 00:38:21.030
people reach out whose lives we've touched,

00:38:21.040 --> 00:38:23.510
and you tell us your stories of how

00:38:23.520 --> 00:38:25.750
you say we've brought you

00:38:25.760 --> 00:38:28.069
back to Jesus

00:38:28.079 --> 00:38:31.430
from France to Germany.

00:38:31.440 --> 00:38:34.230
It's absolutely incredible.

00:38:34.240 --> 00:38:38.470
And I just go,

00:38:38.470 --> 00:38:38.480
'Wow.'I

00:38:38.480 --> 00:38:40.470
truly don't know what to say

00:38:40.480 --> 00:38:42.950
about some of the kindness where people

00:38:42.960 --> 00:38:44.950
say, 'You brought me back to the

00:38:44.950 --> 00:38:44.960
Lord.'I

00:38:44.960 --> 00:38:47.109
was backslidden. I was on

00:38:47.119 --> 00:38:49.270
my way to hell, and now you've taught me

00:38:49.280 --> 00:38:51.190
how to pray and be intimate and be real

00:38:51.200 --> 00:38:53.190
with God. And I don't think there's any

00:38:53.200 --> 00:38:56.390
other way other than just to be real.

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:58.150
I don't like all the charismatic

00:38:58.160 --> 00:39:01.750
flakiness on TV and YouTube and

00:39:01.760 --> 00:39:03.829
Prophet so-and-so and this and that.

00:39:03.839 --> 00:39:05.270
There's only certain people that I'll

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:06.790
listen to or ever talk to on the phone

00:39:06.800 --> 00:39:08.069
because the Lord says, 'Hey, they're

00:39:08.079 --> 00:39:10.390
authentic. You can talk to

00:39:10.390 --> 00:39:10.400
them.'And

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:11.910
you ask me, 'Brandon, who would you give

00:39:11.920 --> 00:39:13.829
your money to? Who would you do this?

00:39:13.839 --> 00:39:15.829
Who would you that?'That's not for me to

00:39:15.839 --> 00:39:18.390
tell you. You have to follow the voice

